<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 06:17:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据《世界报》报道，欧盟军事首脑表示，将欧洲军队派往格陵兰岛是有意义的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-military-chief-says-it-would-make-sense-put-european-troops-greenland-welt-2025-01-25/</link><description>根据德国《周日世界报》周六发表的采访，欧盟最高军事官员罗伯特·布里格表示，在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示有兴趣收购丹麦领土之际，欧盟国家在格陵兰岛驻军是有意义的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 03:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-military-chief-says-it-would-make-sense-put-european-troops-greenland-welt-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾因中国“骚扰”而暂停南海调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-harassing-its-fisheries-boats-south-china-sea-2025-01-25/</link><description>菲律宾周六表示，在其两艘渔船面临中国海警和海军的“骚扰”和侵略行为后，该国已暂停在南海的一项科学调查。</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2025 02:12:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-accuses-china-harassing-its-fisheries-boats-south-china-sea-2025-01-25/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级外交官卢比奥敦促越南解决贸易不平衡问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-urges-vietnam-address-trade-imbalance-2025-01-24/</link><description>美国新任国务卿马可·卢比奥周五与越南副总理兼外交部长裴青山通电话，敦促越南解决贸易失衡问题，并讨论了对中国的共同担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 22:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-urges-vietnam-address-trade-imbalance-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>英国资深议员表示消费者和投资者希望了解中国棉花的真相</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/senior-uk-lawmaker-says-consumers-investors-want-truth-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</link><description>英国议会一个委员会主席周五表示，英国消费者和投资者希望了解英国在线快时尚零售商 Shein 是否销售来自中国新疆省棉花的产品的真相。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/senior-uk-lawmaker-says-consumers-investors-want-truth-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>王告诉卢比奥领导人已经确定了美中关系的基调和方向</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-chinas-wang-speak-first-phone-call-china-says-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周五与美国新任国务卿马可·卢比奥通话，北京方面表示，他告诉这位著名的对华鹰派，美中关系的方向和基调已由两国领导人确定，他希望卢比奥发挥建设性作用为了两国人民的利益。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:36:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-top-diplomat-rubio-chinas-wang-speak-first-phone-call-china-says-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰首相在与中国丁磊会谈时提到ASML</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/dutch-pm-raised-asml-talks-with-chinas-ding-2025-01-24/</link><description>荷兰首相迪克·肖夫周五表示，与来访的中国国务院副总理丁薛祥进行了“重要对话”，其中包括关于人权和半导体设备供应商 ASML 的讨论。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 16:02:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/dutch-pm-raised-asml-talks-with-chinas-ding-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>宝马与中国电动汽车制造商一起向欧盟法院提起关税挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-joins-chinese-ev-makers-filing-eu-court-challenge-tariffs-2025-01-24/</link><description>根据法院网站上的一份文件，宝马已与中国生产商一起向欧盟法院（CJEU）提出质疑，反对欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车（EV）征收关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:33:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/bmw-joins-chinese-ev-makers-filing-eu-court-challenge-tariffs-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾向有争议环礁的军舰发送了物资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-sent-provisions-warship-disputed-atoll-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国海警表示，菲律宾周五派出一艘民用船只，向其“非法搁浅”在南海有争议环礁仁爱礁的军舰运送补给品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:25:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-sent-provisions-warship-disputed-atoll-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>英国高级议员将再次就中国棉花问题致信Shein</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/senior-uk-lawmaker-write-shein-again-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</link><description>英国议会委员会主席计划第二次写信给Shein，再次询问这家在线快时尚零售商是否将含有棉花的产品从中国新疆地区运往英国。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 13:15:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/senior-uk-lawmaker-write-shein-again-china-cotton-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将人工智能、生物技术和廉价能源作为推动全球竞争力的目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/france-pushes-massive-pause-eu-red-tape-amid-us-pressure-2025-01-24/</link><description>路透社看到的欧盟委员会文件草案显示，人工智能、生物技术和负担得起的清洁能源将成为欧盟努力提高欧盟全球竞争力并确保与美国和中国保持同步的重点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:37:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/france-pushes-massive-pause-eu-red-tape-amid-us-pressure-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>Telia 出售马歇尔集团股份，中国洪山公司以 11.5 亿美元收购马歇尔集团股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-hongshan-buys-majority-stake-marshall-group-115-bln-deal-2025-01-24/</link><description>HongShan Capital Group (HSG) 周五表示，已达成协议，收购 Marshall Group 的多数股权，该交易对这家总部位于斯德哥尔摩的音频设备制造商的估值为 11 亿欧元（11.5 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:22:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-hongshan-buys-majority-stake-marshall-group-115-bln-deal-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>Shein告诉英国立法者，不允许在美国销售的产品中使用中国棉花</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</link><description>在线快时尚零售商 Shein 周五表示，要求其合同制造商只能从经批准的地区（不包括中国）采购棉花，用于在其最大市场美国销售产品。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:31:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-details-cotton-sourcing-policy-written-evidence-uk-lawmakers-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商江淮汽车预计2024年净亏损，受大众合资企业打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-jac-expects-2024-net-loss-hit-by-vw-venture-2025-01-24/</link><description>安徽江淮汽车集团（JAC）周五表示，预计 2024 年业绩将出现亏损，理由是其与大众的合资企业业绩疲软。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:20:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-automaker-jac-expects-2024-net-loss-hit-by-vw-venture-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾漫画向儿童讲述南海之战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-comic-book-takes-battle-south-china-sea-children-2025-01-24/</link><description>菲律宾周五推出了一本漫画书，以对抗所谓的有关有争议的南中国海海洋权利的歪曲叙述，此举招致了中国的批评。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:11:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-comic-book-takes-battle-south-china-sea-children-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：随着日本央行加息，美元下跌，欧元区增长，人民币松了口气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-24/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 11:06:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>